{"context":"일상 대화에서","dialogue":[{"speaker":"A","text":"라이트노벨이/가 뭐예요?","romanization":"raiteunobeli/ga mwoyeyo?","translation":"What is \"라이트노벨\"?"},{"speaker":"B","text":"라이트노벨은/는 light novel(이)에요.","romanization":"raiteunobeleun/neun light novel(i)eyo.","translation":"\"라이트노벨\" means \"light novel\"."}]}